events.text: Enjoy your own company because at the end of the day, you are on your own!!!
events.author: Mr. ABC

events.text: The only limit to our realization of tomorrow is our doubts of today.
events.author: Mr. DEF

events.text: Do what you can, with what you have, where you are.
events.author: Mr. GHI

events.text: Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts.
events.author: Mr. JKL

events.text: Hardships often prepare ordinary people for an extraordinary destiny.
events.author: Mrs. MNO

events.text: Believe you can and you're halfway there.
events.author: Mr. PQR

events.text: It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop.
events.author: Mrs. STU

events.text: Don't watch the clock; do what it does. Keep going.
events.author: Mr. VWX

events.text: The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.
events.author: Mrs. YZ

events.text: The best way to predict your future is to create it.
events.author: Mr. ABC
